@Reasoning:
Public entry-point alias for generate_solidity_from_hir. Provides
the 'hir_to_<lang>' naming convention that the translation pipeline
drivers expect when locating backends by symbol name.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation:
Tail-calls generate_solidity_from_hir with the same hir_module
argument.
@End Implementation
Process called "hir_to_solidity" takes hir_module as Integer returns Integer:
    Return proc generate_solidity_from_hir from hir_module
End Process
